{"tid":2279642,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"有人用鬼滅之刃，來諷刺侵侵，我先發現一個道理。","createTime":"2020-11-10T02:30:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-12T06:32:35.000Z","uid":43785,"like":11,"dislike":65,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"2536c662f7da3e94833b744f4e4fef39336efdf1","tid":2279642,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T02:30:53.000Z","msg":"有人用鬼滅炎柱，來諷刺侵侵，我先發現一個道理<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kh2dvz6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkh2dvz6.jpg&h=07cca260&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OmWaxPq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOmWaxPq.jpg&h=25c3a290&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原來輸到仆街。所謂既沒有輸，只係打飛機。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MZLCcP8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMZLCcP8.jpg&h=f4415177&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n炭治郎所謂嘅沒有輸，只係打飛機式精神勝利嘅講法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當日睇漫畫，覺得炎柱打上三好型好勁，<br />\n今日重睇一次，鬼有復原能力根本就唔撚夠打。<br />\n<br />\n炭治郎根本就喺度打飛機，仲打到成地精<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過有一樣野唔同，<br />\n人地侵侵一日未死，都仲可以用法院覆桌，反勝<br />\n<br />\n你炎柱仲點覆桌？？？？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n炭仔話自己贏果PART，真係笑撚死人。"},{"pid":"697e3c54822ce4018422272257fca267f469d45a","tid":2279642,"uid":199227,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T02:31:12.000Z","msg":"yes sir"},{"pid":"d36e62b7086ce40c2e50015a9bd4ea13f543d6ba","tid":2279642,"uid":309822,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"cite